Simple Secure Smart

The organic supply chain of your recruitment process !
From the job definition to the integration of the candidate.
Set up a team, track and select candidates, interview, assess and Integrate.

Simple : It's a constant struggle to simplify. We want Qameha to be so obvious and natural to use that you will wonder how you managed to recruit anyone without it. 
It's web based which means, no IT, no upgrades, no installation.

Smart: At the core we are an HR company. Just check our team members. Qameha's workflow gives you the know how of experienced HR professionnals. 

Secure: Your data is confidential and YOU OWN IT. We use the best hosting solutions and security measures for all accounts. You remain in control of all your data all the time.

Recruiting page

Qameha boosts team work, handles repetitive tasks. Time is saved, Quality is improved at each step of the process. 

Each job opening is setup as a mission with clearly defined roles: a mission owner, a manager and interviewers.

Alerts and stats help you quickly identify risks: candidate sourcing quality and volume, pace of the recruiting process, ....

Know where your candidates come from

There is no waste of time. The workflow rolls on. The next step is always suggested.

The interface is designed to let filter high volumes of applications easily.

You build your own candidate base and become less dependant on job boards

Mission team members from third party companies have a restricted need-to-know only access to the candidates and job openings. 

Qameha is so simple to use that you do not need to train your employees. If they are on Facebook or twitter, they'll know what to do straight away.



Your IT department involvment is not required.

You can access your candidates from any location at any time with a simple internet connection. It works on your mobile phone.

There are no upgrades, no installation., no maintenance.

Your data is backed up everyday on remote location servers

You can back up your data anytime with a simple click.

Our servers are based in Europe.

All accounts have a secure SSH connection.

All accounts have a 30 days free trial period.





